Name: Super Jet Juck
About the game: Explore the world with puzzles, fancy mechanisms and dangerous enemies! Super Jet Juck is a dynamic platformer game full of skirmishes, puzzles and adventures. Join the heroic team - the fearless soldiers Juck and Tom on an exciting and dangerous journey. You can play the game either alone or together on one computer! So, you are the captain of a special unit of the army sent to the study of an abandoned space station. Your task is to destroy all defensive systems that have gone out of control!
